reviewText: Hard to get dvd ... Was glad to find it ... and put this in my collection of DiCaprio films.
This was the last movie I needed for my leo collection and finally got it. Dvd was good quality

It was the only movie with Leonardo DiCaprio that I didn't own because it wasn't released in america but now I have them all, on the negative side everything is in Spanish except for the movie but it's still pretty easy to go through the menu without knowing any Spanish

Fuelled with awaken sexual urges, youngsters spent night out at Don's Plum restaurant, deliberating approaches to trance-gender relations and exercising personal sexual dreams.

Natural performing by then young recent stars makes this clear-student-project film nice to watch on any viewer's own merits.
